graph TD
    DataPolicy[Data Policy] --> Collection[1. Data Collection and Processing]
    DataPolicy --> Rights[2. Data Subjects' Rights]
    DataPolicy --> Security[3. Data Security]
    DataPolicy --> Accountability[4. Accountability and Governance]
    DataPolicy --> Transfers[5. Data Transfers]
    DataPolicy --> Compliance[6. Compliance and Enforcement]
    DataPolicy --> Training[7. Training and Awareness]
    DataPolicy --> Incident[8. Incident Response]
    DataPolicy --> Review[9. Policy Review and Amendments]
    DataPolicy --> Contact[Contact DPO]

    Collection --> LawfulBasis[Lawful Basis]
    Collection --> Transparency[Transparency and Purpose]
    Collection --> Minimization[Data Minimization]
    Collection --> FairProcessing[Fair Processing]

    Rights --> Access[Access and Portability]
    Rights --> Correction[Correction and Deletion]
    Rights --> Restriction[Restriction and Objection]
    Rights --> Exercise[Exercise of Rights]

    Security --> CIA[Confidentiality, Integrity, Availability]
    Security --> Protection[Protection Against Unauthorized Access]
    Security --> Prevention[Breach Prevention and Mitigation]

    Accountability --> DPO[Data Protection Officer]
    Accountability --> Audits[Regular Audits and Reviews]
    Accountability --> Structure[Governance Structure]

    Transfers --> CrossBorder[Cross-Border Transfers]
    Transfers --> Documentation[Documentation and Approval]

    Compliance --> Regulatory[Regulatory Compliance]
    Compliance --> Enforcement[Enforcement Mechanisms]
    Compliance --> Reporting[Reporting and Remediation]

    Training --> Mandatory[Mandatory Training Programs]
    Training --> Continuous[Continuous Awareness]
    Training --> TrainingDocs[Documentation of Training]

    Incident --> Protocol[Breach Response Protocol]
    Incident --> Notification[Notification Requirements]
    Incident --> PostIncident[Post-Incident Review]

    Review --> RegularReview[Regular Review]
    Review --> Communication[Stakeholder Communication]

    Contact --> Email[legal@citruslabs.co.ke]

    subgraph Core Policy Elements
        Collection
        Rights
        Security
        Accountability
    end

    subgraph Operational Elements
        Transfers
        Compliance
        Training
        Incident
    end

    subgraph Management
        Review
        Contact
    end

    style DataPolicy fill:#FF9E1B,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Core Policy Elements fill:#F5F5F5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style Operational Elements fill:#E8E8E8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style Management fill:#F0F0F0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px

    classDef section fill:#1F1F1F,color:#FFFFFF,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    class Collection,Rights,Security,Accountability,Transfers,Compliance,Training,Incident,Review,Contact section